                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="2r" to="6v"/>
                            <title xml:lang="en" type="complete">Additional service of hymns and prayers</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ። ኦእግዚኦ፡ መሐረነ፡ ፲፪ጊዜ፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰበል።</incipit>
                            <note>It is possible that the first quire <locus from="1" to="7"/> constitutes a different unit of production.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        
